<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Ảnh</title>
  <style>
    body{font-family:Segoe UI,system-ui; margin:0; padding:28px; background:#0b0f17; color:#e5e7eb;}
    a{color:#38bdf8; text-decoration:none;}
    .wrap{max-width:1000px; margin:auto;}
    .grid{display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(180px,1fr)); gap:12px;}
    .img{width:100%; aspect-ratio:1/1; object-fit:cover; border-radius:14px; border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12);}
    .hint{opacity:.8;}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrap">
    <p><a href="/">← Quay về trang chủ</a></p>
    <h1>Ảnh</h1>
    <p class="hint">Bạn có thể upload ảnh vào repo và dán link vào các thẻ &lt;img&gt; dưới đây.</p>

    <div class="grid">
      <img class="img" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1520975958225-9ac16b1c5842?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80" alt="Ảnh 1">
      <img class="img" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1520975958225-9ac16b1c5842?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80" alt="Ảnh 2">
      <img class="img" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1520975958225-9ac16b1c5842?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80" alt="Ảnh 3">
      <img class="img" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1520975958225-9ac16b1c5842?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80" alt="Ảnh 4">
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
